N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5100.6 - Practice where regulations do not govern

State Regulations

In any matter not governed by these regulations, the
commission shall exercise the commission's discretion so as to carry out the
commission's purposes. Notes
